<i>♪ O, kekasih ♪</i>

00:10:13.885 --> 00:10:20.951
<i>♪ O, kekasih ♪</i>

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.033
Aku tahu...

00:10:33.084 --> 00:10:34.516
Kita tidak bersama lagi.

00:10:40.012 --> 00:10:41.489
Tapi hatiku

00:10:43.265 --> 00:10:44.533
masih belum sadar.

00:10:45.622 --> 00:10:46.755
Jadi tolong,

00:10:48.168 --> 00:10:51.276
biarkan aku membodohi hatiku sedikit lebih lama.

00:10:54.625 --> 00:10:55.867
Aku tahu...

00:10:57.566 --> 00:10:59.400
Bukankah hatimu seharusnya

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:02.969
untuk melupakan saya dalam 21 detik?

00:11:04.789 --> 00:11:06.321
Dan itu masih belum tahu.

00:11:06.401 --> 00:11:07.572
Diam saja.

00:11:13.794 --> 00:11:14.646
Halo Pak.

00:11:14.726 --> 00:11:17.253
